reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is the perfect sizeAll my stuff fits nice n simple to find and the side pockets are great for cell phone and keysThe price also not bad2 design straps a bonusStyle good for church wearing/LOVE IT🤎

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love the straps
reviews.reviewText: This is a really nice purse. It’s durable and a good size- would be able to even hold a small water bottle. The colorful straps are my favorite part. The only down side for me is that I prefer a purse with more dividers and differentiated pockets to keep it organized.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for Traveling
reviews.reviewText: I bought this to use on my trip to Mexico. This was just perfect. It is roomy, easy to change the straps, cute, and has the capacity to hold small souvenirs. The price was hard to beat as well. I will be buying this again in a few other colors.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is an amazing crossbody purse. Soft, lightweight and beautiful. I am very pleased!!!! I love the length of the strap. I can easily go long or shorter. IN LOVE!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars You will need to get another strap
reviews.reviewText: The faux print strap is the worst thing about this purse. I would recommend getting another. The purse is soft and stylish. Lots of pockets to organize. It's cross body but the strap is not adjustable. I recommend another.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Quality is the most important to know if this
reviews.reviewText: This bag is made of good quality and it has a nice size inside so that you can fit many items in including your phone. This is a good product for the price and it comes with two interchangeable straps.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars So glad I bought it
reviews.reviewText: It’s exactly what I have been looking for. I love that it looks and feels like leather but without the cost of leather, I bought the color A-Brown. It’s not only looks great but it’s functional, lots of places for different items.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Great but strap is not the best
reviews.reviewText: The purse is great. The strap is made of a fabric that has a slick feel to it. So the adjustable strap always loosens all the way. Have to readjust constantly. Disappointed because I loved the purse.
